data.enText: one of the four pointed teeth in the front of a human's or animal's mouth

simple_means.memory_skill: can 犬 + ine 具有…性质的，如…的 → 犬的

tr: any of various fissiped mammals with nonretractile claws and typically long muzzles
one of the four pointed conical teeth (two in each jaw) located between the incisors and the premolars
of or relating to or characteristic of members of the family Canidae
of or relating to a pointed conical tooth

value.def: Canine teeth or canines are pointed teeth near the front of the mouth of humans and of some animals.
